                                    jcr:title="Our Principles"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                    type="h3"/>
                                <text
                                    cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                    jcr:created="{Date}2022-11-28T14:12:33.220-05:00"
                                    jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                    jcr:lastModified="{Date}2025-10-28T00:03:24.082-04:00"
                                    jcr:lastModifiedBy="nandivx5"
                                    jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Our purpose is profound, and our path is clear. We embrace the responsibility of making a remarkable impact on people's lives through the innovative medicines and solutions we create together. This is driven by our compassion for people, commitment to innovation and inclusion, service to the community, and uncompromising integrity at the heart of everything we do.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Operating as one AbbVie team, we care deeply for our patients, their families, our employees, and our communities. We strive to always do the right thing, pursuing the highest standards in quality, compliance, safety, and performance. In everything we do, we invest and innovate relentlessly to tackle unmet needs, creating new medicines and healthcare approaches for a healthier world.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                    textIsRich="true"/>
                            </container>
                        </par_12>
